  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Story</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A group of friends find themselves stuck in an old house during a thunderstorm. They discover a strange fertility themed board game and decide to humor it. As the game goes on, they start experiencing nausea, fatigue, and other unusual symptoms. They laugh it off, until eventually one girl's stomach visibly swells.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Separated from the rest of the world, their only option is to continue playing and hope things revert back to normal when someone wins.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In summary, a Jumanji inspiration, with a dark twist and a focus on pregnancy and fertility.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gameplay</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gameplay consists of navigating through the house, interacting with the other characters and solving occasional puzzles in order to progress the story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Three branching paths are available.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Completing all three routes unlocks Free Play mode, which functions as a dynamic board game with character commentary.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208160/extras/c2b9300cfa0e64aff9f61d69b0137de7.poster.avif?t=1730067060\" width=450 height=512 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208160/extras/c2b9300cfa0e64aff9f61d69b0137de7.webm?t=1730067060\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208160/extras/c2b9300cfa0e64aff9f61d69b0137de7.mp4?t=1730067060\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Yuri </strong>is a sarcastic and cynical individual. She's cold and aloof, but deep down she cares about her friends. She's not afraid to speak her mind and is blunt when giving advice.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208160/extras/495d61f4d3bda2c6ae80567d5ab1b7e2.poster.avif?t=1730067060\" width=450 height=512 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208160/extras/495d61f4d3bda2c6ae80567d5ab1b7e2.webm?t=1730067060\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208160/extras/495d61f4d3bda2c6ae80567d5ab1b7e2.mp4?t=1730067060\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Kari </strong>is a flirtatious and mischievous girl. She's popular and well-liked, and her cheerful attitude is infectious. However, she has a tendency to get bored easily and seek out new thrills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208160/extras/69d4268100b3f3cf41e18bc76c9eaeb9.poster.avif?t=1730067060\" width=450 height=512 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208160/extras/69d4268100b3f3cf41e18bc76c9eaeb9.webm?t=1730067060\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208160/extras/69d4268100b3f3cf41e18bc76c9eaeb9.mp4?t=1730067060\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Nanami </strong>is shy and timid. She's used to being ignored or teased by her friends. She's careful and cautious, and doesn't jump into things without thinking.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Story</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A group of friends find themselves stuck in an old house during a thunderstorm. They discover a strange fertility themed board game and decide to humor it. As the game goes on, they start experiencing nausea, fatigue, and other unusual symptoms. They laugh it off, until eventually one girl's stomach visibly swells.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Separated from the rest of the world, their only option is to continue playing and hope things revert back to normal when someone wins.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In summary, a Jumanji inspiration, with a dark twist and a focus on pregnancy and fertility.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gameplay</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gameplay consists of navigating through the house, interacting with the other characters and solving occasional puzzles in order to progress the story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Three branching paths are available.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Completing all three routes unlocks Free Play mode, which functions as a dynamic board game with character commentary.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208160/extras/c2b9300cfa0e64aff9f61d69b0137de7.poster.avif?t=1730067060\" width=450 height=512 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208160/extras/c2b9300cfa0e64aff9f61d69b0137de7.webm?t=1730067060\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208160/extras/c2b9300cfa0e64aff9f61d69b0137de7.mp4?t=1730067060\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Yuri </strong>is a sarcastic and cynical individual. She's cold and aloof, but deep down she